creator: Donatella Studio
descriptionHtml:
Screen Mirroring: Cast to TV app is an extremely smart tool that helps you control all your devices easily and quickly.
Screen Mirroring: Chromecast, cast to TV, helps you cast phone screen to big TV screen in high quality. You can easily cast to TV all types of media files, including mobile games, photos, music, videos & E-books and watch on the big screen.

All your devices are supported:
• Chromecast
• Roku, Roku Stick, and Roku TVs
• Most smart TVs: Hisense, Samsung, LG, Sony, Panasonic, TLC, Toshiba, etc.
• Xbox, Fire TV, and Fire Stick
• Other DLNA receivers

Guide to mirror your mobile screen to smart TV with screen mirroring TV:
1. Your TV should support Wireless Display or any sort of Display Dongles.
2. The TV must be connected to WI-FI network same as your phone.
3. Download and run smart view Cast to TV and Screen Mirroring App.
4. Enjoy streaming your phone to TV!

Hopefully you will have a relaxing time with this wonderful screen mirroring application.

descriptionHtml:
Are you tired of crowding around small screens to share your favorite photos and videos with friends and family?
Welcome to the Smart TV Cast: Screen Share app for wasting your images, videos, and audio to your TV screen. With its comprehensive features, this web video cast app allows you to enjoy a seamless and immersive media experience in the comfort of your own home.

Key Features in anyview cast app:
👉 TV Mirror: Cast to TV
The screen mirror app allows you to replicate your mobile device or computer screen on your smart TV in real-time. It's perfect for presentations, gaming, or simply browsing the web on a larger display. Share your device screen with friends and family, making group activities more engaging.

👉 Cast Image:
Whether it's your latest vacation photos, a beautiful family portrait, or captivating snapshots from your camera roll, the screen cast app allows you to effortlessly cast images from your mobile device or computer to your smart TV. Share your cherished memories with friends and family on the big screen.

👉 Cast Video:
With this cast to tv app, you can stream videos in high-definition quality directly to your smart TV. Whether it's a movie, TV show, or a homemade video, this tv mirror app supports a wide range of video formats, ensuring that you can enjoy your content without compatibility issues.

👉 Cast Audio:
Turn your living room into a concert hall or party venue with the smart screen share app. Stream your favorite music, podcasts, or audiobooks to your smart TV's superior speakers for a truly immersive audio experience.

👉 Cast on Web:
The web cast app isn't limited to just mobile devices; it also offers a web-based platform. By visiting the app website on your computer's browser, you can easily cast multimedia content to your smart TV without the need for additional installations or extensions.

With this connect to tv app, your smart TV becomes the hub for all your multimedia content, making it easy to share, enjoy, and entertain. Say goodbye to the limitations of small screens and embrace the convenience and joy of casting your favorite content on the big screen with this versatile video tv cast app.

Experience the power of cast video to screen app and enjoy the convenience, versatility, and immersive media experience it brings to your home. Thank you!
